===Letter===
'''נ''' (spelled ''[[nun]]'') is the fourteenth letter of the [[Hebrew]] alphabet.<br>
'''ן''' is the final form of the letter ([[sofeet]]), used only at the end of a word.

נ also represents the [[numeral]] 50 in Hebrew numbering.

* '''Last''': [[מ]]
* '''Next''': [[ס]]

